BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:9akXg4xi9w0_siW6zhSpW
SUMMARY:Daybreak Star Community 5K Run and Walk
DTSTAMP:20260214T003547Z
DTSTART:20260215T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join the community for a series of monthly 5K runs and walks he
	ld at the historic Daybreak Star Indian Cultural Center. This free event w
	elcomes participants of all levels\, from competitive runners to those who
	 enjoy a leisurely walk through beautiful scenery. \n\nEvent Schedule \n\n
	Events take place on the 3rd Sunday of each month. Please note the followi
	ng upcoming dates: \n\nFebruary 15th\n\nMarch 15th\n\nApril 19th\n\nMay 17
	th\n\nJune 21st\n\nJuly 19th \\(37th Annual Indian Days Powwow Weekend\, s
	tarting at 9:00 AM\\)\n\nTiming and Location Details \n\nStart Time: 10:00
	 AM\n\nLocation: Daybreak Star Indian Cultural Center \\(5011 Bernie White
	bear Way Seattle\, WA 98199\\)\n\nMeeting Point: Meet at the Powwow Ground
	s\n\nThis event is FREE for all! \n\nLace up your shoes and enjoy the scen
	ic trails while connecting with the community! For more information about 
	the venue and organizing group\, please email communications@unitedindians
	.org
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/daybreak-star-community-5
	k-run-and-walk/18125951/2026-02-15T00
LOCATION:Daybreak Star Indian Cultural Center\, 5011 Bernie Whitebear Way\,
	 Seattle\, WA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:qzQwt84gr0RTockGaNo1M
SUMMARY:Take one of 15 Historic Seattle Walking Tours Today!
DTSTAMP:20260214T003547Z
DTSTART:20260215T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Event Overview  Turbo charge your enthusiasm for WA History by 
	selecting one of 15 self-guided walks organized by Historic Seattle. Choic
	es include: Seattle Central Waterfront\, Pike Place Market Architecture\, 
	Pioneer Square\, Belltown\, Market to MOHAI\, and more! Each walk will tak
	e 1-2 hours\, depending on your group size\, stride length\, steps per min
	ute\, your luck at getting green crosswalk signals\, and how many coffee s
	tops you make along the way:-\\)  Not every walk is a loop\, so the tour m
	ay not end at or near the departure. A map and narrated tour makes it easy
	 to plan and follow.
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/take-one-of-15-historic-s
	eattle-walking-tours-today/18066386/2026-02-15T00
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
